{"tid":1296072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《香港小冊子》招兵買馬","createTime":"2019-07-08T08:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T13:46:19.000Z","uid":272538,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7185632348d9e45368d10fec98562b7bf3fb3b","tid":1296072,"uid":272538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:51:00.000Z","msg":"我們是一班希望透過軟性再教育令香港進步嘅網民。希望利用這個暑假（因為而家已經係暑假，同埋覺得可能可以多啲人幫到手）製作一份「愛香港小冊子」，內容包括：<br />\n-強調我地熱愛香港<br />\n-用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>淺白文字</strong></span>總結香港呢22年內發生嘅大事<br />\n-呢啲事點樣影響香港同市民嘅生活，俾大家知道<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>嚴重性同急切性</strong></span>（所謂嘅50年不變喺過去嘅22年已經好大嘅變遷）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼上一個post後招兵買馬之後（<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1277759/page/1），\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1277759/page/1），</a><br />\n我們而家有大約十人工作，但希望更多人可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">盡快加入</span></strong></span>同提供技術支援，發揮小宇宙，提供意見及分擔工作量。 <br />\n<br />\n以下提供我地group設計嘅一啲暫時的草稿，等大家想像到會係點，歡迎提供意見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7iCeKLh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7iCeKLh.jpg&h=294f622a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tF6jbqh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtF6jbqh.jpg&h=c3be237d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果有其他嘅事件想我哋喺小冊子入面都提及嘅話，亦可以提出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣請先加入tg group：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/L9cAohYnxEkntvtQYZpznw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FL9cAohYnxEkntvtQYZpznw&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=76845f5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/L9cAohYnxEkntvtQYZpznw</a><br />\n<br />\n加入了後會提供驗證方法，然後再加到另一個安全頻道。謝謝大家。"},{"pid":"a0e097f3cad2b00f8d65ef5c645d0fa6190fa4a4","tid":1296072,"uid":191656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好!"},{"pid":"4d79917470e0ac8e76609e36a685ebb87888a29f","tid":1296072,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1295342/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1295342/</a><br />\n[英文速譯] 綜合大量警察嚴重違規行為"},{"pid":"136bb10018491dfcad20787b498fc480a93d9112","tid":1296072,"uid":264380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:02:45.000Z","msg":"<code>我冇野講 我唔解鎖 我要搵律師 (背定律師電話) 我唔簽任何文件 我要警誡記錄 我要食飯 飲水 毛氈 去廁所 我唔舒服要去醫院 我要睇你委任證同編號投訴你</code><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />皮已正<br />\n<code>我要報案，我要告佢，我係目擊證人，我要拎落案警員number同案件編號RN(Reference Number)。記得報案要全程拍住片影埋警察樣同number，警察如果唔處理都有得追究。</code>"},{"pid":"b1b479356b6f6f1309184b2bcc5cfc90e56a3905","tid":1296072,"uid":264380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推！！！"},{"pid":"215fd81684a03caf92157cd3ae4bbf292b526068","tid":1296072,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78703206d49091c259cd87075160b049101dc41","tid":1296072,"uid":264380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/